OL,3,CCharity which helps people in crisis
OL,4,Cis to close at the end of the year
OL,6,FA charity in Newquay, Cornwall which
OL,7,Fhelps people in crisis will close its
OL,8,Fdoors for the final time at the end of
OL,9,Fthe year.
OL,11,FNewquay DISC is a drop in centre and
OL,12,Ffoodbank service which makes free
OL,13,Fmeals for thousands of people.
OL,15,FEarlier this year the charity received
OL,16,FThe King's Award for Voluntary
OL,17,FService. However founder Monique
OL,18,FCollins announced in October that she
OL,19,Fwas stepping down after 7 years.
