OL,3,CCharity which helps people in crisis
OL,4,Cis to close at the end of the year
OL,6,FIn a statement the trustees say it is
OL,7,Fwith a heavy heart they have decided
OL,8,Fto close on the 1st January. The
OL,9,Fstatement thanked all the volunteers
OL,10,Fwho helped run their service and
OL,11,Fencouraged the community to keep
OL,12,Fsupporting those in need.
OL,14,FHere is the statement in full: "With a
OL,15,Fheavy heart the Trustees are
OL,16,Fannouncing the closure from 1st
OL,17,FJanuary 2025 of DISC Newquay, a cause
OL,18,Fthat has been at the centre of a
OL,19,Fmission to support and uplift the most
OL,20,Fvulnerable in our society.
OL,26,@vD@`OU
