OL,3,CCharity which helps people in crisis
OL,4,Cis to close at the end of the year
OL,6,F"While it is incredibly difficult to
OL,7,Fsay goodbye, we are proud of all that
OL,8,Fthe charity has accomplished. DISC has
OL,9,Fhelped thousands of people regain
OL,10,Ftheir dignity, access essential
OL,11,Fresources, and, perhaps most
OL,12,Fimportantly, feel seen and cared for.
OL,14,F"The kindness and commitment from the
OL,15,Fvolunteers made this work possible,
OL,16,Fand for that, we are deeply grateful.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
