OL,3,CCharity which helps people in crisis
OL,4,Cis to close at the end of the year
OL,6,F"As the landscape of charitable giving
OL,7,Fand need evolves, the decision to
OL,8,Fclose was not made lightly, but a
OL,9,Fdecision needed to be made. We are
OL,10,Fhowever confident that the values of
OL,11,Fcompassion and community that we've
OL,12,Fchampioned over the years will
OL,13,Fcontinue to live on.
OL,15,F"We are deeply grateful to the
OL,16,Fvolunteers, donors, partners, and
OL,17,Feveryone who believed in our mission
OL,18,Fand worked tirelessly for the good of
OL,19,Fthe local community.
