OL,3,CCharity which helps people in crisis
OL,4,Cis to close at the end of the year
OL,6,F"Although this chapter is coming to an
OL,7,Fend, we know that the spirit of this
OL,8,Forganisation will persist in the
OL,9,Fhearts of those DISC helped, and the
OL,10,Fvolunteers that gave their time.
OL,12,F"We encourage the community to
OL,13,Fcontinue supporting those in need,
OL,14,Fwhether through other local
OL,15,Forganisations, acts of kindness, or by
OL,16,Fbeing the change you want to see.
OL,26,@tD@AOU
