OL,3,CCharity which helps people in crisis
OL,4,Cis to close at the end of the year
OL,6,F"Thank you, from the bottom of our
OL,7,Fhearts, for believing in DISC and for
OL,8,Fmaking such a profound difference.
OL,9,FYour generosity has left an indelible
OL,10,Fmark on our community, and for that,
OL,11,Fwe are eternally grateful."
